           Btn_Revert:LABEL IN FRAME Dialog-Frame = "&Revert".

&IF '{&WINDOW-SYSTEM}' EQ 'TTY':U &THEN
    RUN assignHelp.
&ENDIF

    DISABLE Btn_Save Btn_Revert WITH FRAME Dialog-Frame.
    ENABLE BrowseList Btn_Cancel WITH FRAME Dialog-Frame.

